在她的第一张专辑发行之后，她的母唱片公司[[EMI|EMI]]被{{tsl|en|Terra Firma Capital Partners||Terra Firma}}接管。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.contactmusic.com/news.nsf/article/allen%20attacks%20emis%20owners%20terra%20firma_1091153|title=Allen Attacks EMI's Owners Terra Firma|work=WENN|date=8 January 2009|accessdate=22 September 2014}}</ref> 她也将她的管理公司由Artist Management更换为Twenty-First Artists——尽管她的核心团队仍然存在。在其唱片公司的迫切要求之下，莉莉试图与若干作词人和制作人制作专辑，却以失败告终。最终莉莉转头向当时为专辑《Alright, Still》写了三首歌的{{tsl|en|Greg Kurstin||Greg Kurstin}} 求助。<ref name="Uncertain Smile">{{cite news|last=Heath|first=Chris|date=16 January 2009|title=Lily Allen – Uncertain Smile|work=The Daily Telegraph|location=London|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/4223221/Llly-Allen-uncertain-smile.html|accessdate=22 September 2014}}</ref> 专辑在洛杉矶的Eagle Rock工作室中由Kurstin制作。<ref name=USrelease/> 在回到Kus之前，莉莉和Kurstin一同写下了那些歌曲，而后者为歌曲提供了钢琴音轨。这相较于她早期作品中自行创作歌词、完成音轨的做法有所变化。<ref name="papermag">{{cite web|url=http://www.papermag.com/?section=article&parid=2775&page=1|title=Girl Gone Wild Lily Allen, Reflects, Owns up and Moves On|publisher=Papermag.com|accessdate=22 September 2014|archive-date=2018-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116165722/http://www.papermag.com/?section=article&parid=2775&page=1|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 莉莉曾表示：“我们决定尝试制作反响更大的歌曲、更多空灵和真实的歌曲……我想自始至终与一个人合作，以保证作品的一体化。我希望它给我一种拥有真诚感觉。我认为我成长了，希望作品能够有所体现。”<ref name=USrelease/> 她在她的MySpace页面上上传了两份新曲小样，并计划发行一张[[混音带|混音带]]，以告知其粉丝其新发展方向。<ref>Salmon, Chris (25 April 2008). [http://arts.guardian.co.uk/filmandmusic/story/0,,2275788,00.html Click to download], ''The Guardian''</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://nymag.com/daily/entertainment/2008/04/lily_allen_expresses_profound.html|title=Lily Allen Expresses Profound Disappointment in Self New York Magazine|work=New York Magazine|date=18 April 2008|accessdate=24 July 2011|archive-date=2009-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090924050940/http://nymag.com/daily/entertainment/2008/04/lily_allen_expresses_profound.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report_allen-gets-dark-and-introspective-in-new-album_1160412|title=Allen gets dark and introspective in new album – Entertainment|work=<!-- 页面不存在 -->[[每日新闻与分析|DNA]]|agency={{tsl|en|Indo-Asian News Service||IANS}}|date=19 April 2008|accessdate=12 September 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.guardian.co.uk/observermusic/2008/04/new_lily.html|title=New Lily|work=The Guardian|accessdate=22 September 2014|archive-date=2008-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080622004200/http://blogs.guardian.co.uk/observermusic/2008/04/new_lily.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://people.com/celebrity/lily-allen-leaks-her-own-songs-on-the-internet/|title=Lily Allen Leaks Her Own Songs on the Internet|last=Weiss|first=Shari|work=<!-- 页面不存在 -->[[人物_(雜誌)|People]]|date=18 April 2008|accessdate=7 September 2018|archive-date=2018-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180830074032/https://people.com/celebrity/lily-allen-leaks-her-own-songs-on-the-internet/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

莉莉取消了原定于2008年[[怀特岛音乐节|怀特岛音乐节]]的演出，并告诉音乐节主办人John Giddings她取消计划的原因是她的专辑晚于计划。 Giddings说道这个给出的理由让人不能接受，很可能是谎话。不过Giddings并未决定对她依法索要赔偿。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7279554.stm|title=Allen snub angers festival boss|publisher=BBC News|date=5 March 2008|accessdate=22 September 2014|archive-date=2020-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200627021339/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7279554.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 她在[[戛纳电影节|戛纳电影节]]中醉酒与上身裸体的照片也在新闻界广泛报道。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/lily-allen-244-1321896|title=Lily Allen addresses Cannes Controversy|work=NME|date=23 May 2008|accessdate=9 June 2019|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609010702/https://www.nme.com/news/music/lily-allen-244-1321896|dead-url=no}}</ref> 她在2008年{{Le|Glamour|Glamour (magazine)}}颁奖典礼上的演出也受到了批评，因为她醉酒登台、身着印有断头的[[小鹿斑比|小鹿斑比]]形象的裙子，并在台上与[[艾爾頓·約翰|艾尔顿·约翰]]进行了包含粗话的交流。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/gossip/2008/06/04/2008-06-04_oh_deer_lily_allens_no_bambi_fan.html |title=Oh, deer! Lily Allen's no Bambi fan |work=Daily News |location=New York |date=4 June 2008 |accessdate=24 July 2011 |first=Korin |last=Miller |archive-date=2009-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090822090400/http://www.nydailynews.com/gossip/2008/06/04/2008-06-04_oh_deer_lily_allens_no_bambi_fan.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Tapper |first=Christina |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20204414,00.html |title=Lily Allen Calls Drunken Behaviour 'Embarrassing' |work=People |date=4 June 2008 |accessdate=24 July 2011 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303194555/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20204414,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/music/article4666463.ece|title=Elton John and Lily Allen in war of words at GQ awards|last=Schmidt|first=Veronica|work=The Times|location=London|date=3 September 2008|accessdate=22 July 2011|archive-date=2010-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100208142616/http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/music/article4666463.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2008年6月29日，莉莉与制作人马克·荣森一同于[[格拉斯顿伯里当代表演艺术节|格拉斯顿伯里艺术节]]上表演。由于（外）祖母不巧前夜去世，莉莉动情地为（外）祖母献唱了《{{tsl|en|Littlest Things||Littlest Things}}》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.contactmusic.com/news.nsf/article/show%20goes%20on%20for%20grieving%20allen_1072867|title=Lily Allen – Show goes on for grieving Allen|publisher=WENN|accessdate=22 September 2014|archive-date=2009-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090113014021/http://www.contactmusic.com/news.nsf/article/show%20goes%20on%20for%20grieving%20allen_1072867|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[干我屁事|与我无关]]》原定于2008年初发行，但因为她的流产与创意问题而延期至秋季发行。2008年秋，EMI经历了公司重组。这导致了专辑的发行日期更改。<ref name=Billboard090117>{{cite web|url=http://billboard.biz/bbbiz/content_display/magazine/features/e3iaed899a63b67b209fd2b3b0b9554c4dc?imw=Y |title=English Beat: Lily Allen |work=Billboard |date=17 January 2009 |accessdate=24 July 2011}}</ref><ref name="26Feb">{{cite news |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2009/02/26/chart-enw-euro-albums-idUKN2629541420090226 |title=European Top Albums |agency=Reuters |date=26 February 2009 |accessdate=24 July 2011 |archive-date=2015-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150701111530/http://uk.reuters.com/article/2009/02/26/chart-enw-euro-albums-idUKN2629541420090226 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 针对不知道莉莉或她专辑的群体，Matmi制作了一款名为《Escape the Fear》的网络游戏，进行[[病毒营销|病毒营销]]。<ref>[http://www.gamesdog.co.uk/news/news.phtml/8500/9524/Lily-Allen-game-promote-album.phtml Lily Allen promotes new album with casual game] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamesdog.co.uk/news/news.phtml/8500/9524/Lily-Allen-game-promote-album.phtml |date=20140403100729 }} 18 December 2008</ref> 该游戏发布以来，三次登顶全球热门游戏排行榜，其中包括全年最具竞争力的圣诞节所在周。截至2009年2月18日，该游戏已被游玩超过二百万次。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.newswiretoday.com/news/46727/|title=Lily Allen Online Game Passes Two Million Plays As Single & Album Top the Music Charts|publisher=Newswiretoday.com|date=19 February 2009|accessdate=29 October 2018|archive-date=2020-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200629235406/https://www.newswiretoday.com/news/46727/|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 莉莉和[[衝擊合唱團|冲撞乐队]]的吉他手{{tsl|en|Mick Jones (The Clash)||Mick Jones}}为慈善专辑《{{tsl|en|Heroes (2009 album)||Heroes}}》表演了冲撞乐队专辑里的歌曲《{{tsl|en|Straight to Hell (song)||Straight to Hell}}》。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.spin.com/2009/01/beck-lily-allen-tv-radio-cover-rock-legends/|title=Beck, Lily Allen, TV on the Radio Cover Rock Legends|work=<!-- 页面不存在 -->[[Spin_(雜誌)|Spin]]|date=12 January 2009|accessdate=22 September 2014|archive-date=2020-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200127130700/https://www.spin.com/2009/01/beck-lily-allen-tv-radio-cover-rock-legends/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

