专辑《与我无关》发行于2009年2月。一经发布便空降英国、加拿大和澳大利亚榜首，美国第五。<ref name="USrelease">{{cite web|url=http://www.nme.com/news/lily-allen/40732|title=Lily Allen announces US release of second album|date=29 October 2008|work=NME|accessdate=22 September 2014|archive-date=2016-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822004346/http://www.nme.com/news/lily-allen/40732|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="doubleone">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/269402/lily-allen-asserts-control-over-uk-charts|title=Lily Allen Asserts Control Over UK Charts|date=16 February 2009|work=Billboard|accessdate=22 September 2014|archive-date=2019-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129235723/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/269402/lily-allen-asserts-control-over-uk-charts|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=USdebut>[http://billboard.biz/bbbiz/content_display/charts/chart_alert/e3i39dad3309e171bf915abfbd43f89a0f2?imw=Y Grammies And Valentine's Day Warm Up The Chart] {{Wayback|url=http://billboard.biz/bbbiz/content_display/charts/chart_alert/e3i39dad3309e171bf915abfbd43f89a0f2?imw=Y |date=20110813001212 }} ''Billboard'' 18 February 2009</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://jam.canoe.ca/Music/Artists/A/Allen_Lily/2009/02/18/8437821-jam.html|title=Lily Allen debuts at No. 1|work=canoe.ca|accessdate=22 September 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20120710051542/http://jam.canoe.ca/Music/Artists/A/Allen_Lily/2009/02/18/8437821-jam.html|archivedate=10 July 2012}}</ref><ref name="Voice">{{cite web|url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/entertainment/music/poster-girl-tag-is-not-me-says-lily-allen/2009/03/04/1235842456531.html|title=Lily Allen says poster girl tag is Not Me|work=The Sydney Morning Herald|accessdate=22 September 2014|archive-date=2017-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201153053/http://www.smh.com.au/news/entertainment/music/poster-girl-tag-is-not-me-says-lily-allen/2009/03/04/1235842456531.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 该专辑销量在英国获得白金认证。<ref name=platinum>[http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/content_display/industry/e3i9659c5aa3ebf280695c7989efd1c73a4 Lily Allen Adds U.K. Dates] ''Billboard'' 22 May 2009</ref> 该专辑的发售帮助[[EMI|EMI]]公司将其收入翻了三番。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/mediatechnologyandtelecoms/5292343/EMI-looks-to-the-Dark-Side-to-grow-games-presence.html|title=EMI looks to the Dark Side to grow games presence|date=7 May 2009|work=The Daily Telegraph|accessdate=22 September 2014|archive-date=2019-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129235802/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/mediatechnologyandtelecoms/5292343/EMI-looks-to-the-Dark-Side-to-grow-games-presence.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 专辑的第一首单曲〈The Fear〉发售仅四周后便于英国登顶。<ref name="TheFear4">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/269363/kings-of-leon-lily-allen-top-uk-charts|title=Kings of Leon, Lily Allen|date=23 February 2009|work=Billboard|accessdate=22 September 2014|archive-date=2020-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116002629/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/269363/kings-of-leon-lily-allen-top-uk-charts|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/269444/lily-allen-springsteen-retain-uk-chart-peaks|title=Lily Allen, Springsteen Retain UK Chart Peaks|date=9 February 2009|work=Billboard|accessdate=22 September 2014|archive-date=2019-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630013434/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/269444/lily-allen-springsteen-retain-uk-chart-peaks|dead-url=no}}</ref> 专辑的第二首单曲〈{{tsl|en|Not Fair||Not Fair}}〉达到第九名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/268794/lady-gaga-tinchy-stryder-top-uk-charts|title=Lady GaGa, Tinchy Stryder Top UK Charts|date=27 April 2009|work=Billboard|accessdate=22 September 2014|archive-date=2019-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129235708/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/268794/lady-gaga-tinchy-stryder-top-uk-charts|dead-url=no}}</ref> 她于三月开始了为期两年的《{{tsl|en|It's Not Me, It's You World Tour|与我无关 (世界巡回演唱会)|与我无关}}》世界巡回演唱会，2010年9月巡演收官。该专辑中她与{{tsl|en|Greg Kurstin||Greg Kurstin}}合作的作品使她获得了2010年艾弗·诺韦洛奖的“年度词曲作者”奖项。另外，莉莉与Kurstin还因〈The Fear〉赢得了“最佳词曲歌曲奖”和“最佳表演作品奖”（英语：''Most Performed Work''）莉莉称这些奖项为“真正的奖项”并对能够获此殊荣倍感激动。<ref name="Novello">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/958177/lily-allen-wins-three-ivors|title=Lily Allen Wins Three Ivors|date=20 May 2010|work=Billboard|accessdate=22 September 2014|archive-date=2019-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129235710/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/958177/lily-allen-wins-three-ivors|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2010年10月，莉莉因其歌曲《The Fear》在美国电台的广泛播放而第二次赢得了来自美国的[[廣播音樂公司|BMI]]流行音乐奖。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-238712518.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121115145621/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-238712518.html |dead-url=yes |archive-date=15 November 2012 |title=Well-played radio stars Glasgow |work=<!-- 页面不存在 -->[[每日紀事報|Daily Record]]|publisher={{tsl|en|HighBeam Research||HighBeam Research}} |date=8 October 2010 |accessdate=12 September 2012}} {{Subscription required|date=September 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-11483801 |title=Lily Allen and Sting win music industry awards |work=BBC News |date=6 October 2010 |accessdate=24 July 2011 |archive-date=2019-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190413061403/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-11483801 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

作为[[國家肖像館|英国国家肖像馆]]市场营销活动的一部分，莉莉被任命为其代言人。照片由{{tsl|en|Nadav Kander||Nadav Kander}}拍摄，并鲜明地印刷着“歌手、词作家、花匠”（英语："Vocalist, lyricist, Florist"）字样。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.marieclaire.co.uk/news/celebrity/343699/lily-allen-as-you-ve-never-seen-her-before.html|title=Lily Allen as you never seen her before|work=Marie Claire|accessdate=22 September 2014|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303200352/http://www.marieclaire.co.uk/news/celebrity/343699/lily-allen-as-you-ve-never-seen-her-before.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 莉莉与{{tsl|en|The Kills||The Kills}}乐队的吉他手Jamie Hince为儿童慈善组织The Hoping Foundation募集了48,350英镑善款。 二人在一场[[卡拉OK|卡拉OK]]慈善募捐活动中演唱了《{{tsl|en|Dream a Little Dream of Me||Dream a Little Dream of Me}}》。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/celebritynews/5578325/Supermodel-Kate-Moss-performs-with-Pink-Floyd-guitarist-David-Gilmour-for-charity.html|title=Supermodel Kate Moss performs with Pink Floyd guitarist David Gilmour for charity|date=19 June 2009|work=The Daily Telegraph|accessdate=22 September 2014|archive-date=2010-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101114161350/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/celebritynews/5578325/Supermodel-Kate-Moss-performs-with-Pink-Floyd-guitarist-David-Gilmour-for-charity.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[香奈儿|香奈儿]]的首席设计师[[卡爾·拉格斐|卡尔·拉格斐]]以个人身份雇佣了莉莉并为其拍照，以作为推广其将于2009年9月启动的奢侈手包产品线的手段。<ref>{{cite web |last=Gilbert |first=Laurelle |url=http://www.elleuk.com/star-style/news/node_330751 |title=Lily Allen, the new face of Chanel |work=[[ELLE|Elle]] |date=6 May 2009 |accessdate=12 September 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140403100612/http://www.elleuk.com/star-style/news/node_330751 |archive-date=2014-04-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.monstersandcritics.com/people/news/article_1474460.php/Karl_Lagerfeld_selects_Lily_Allen_for_Chanel_handbag_layout |title=Karl Lagerfeld selects Lily Allen for Chanel handbag layout |publisher=Monsters and Critics |date=1 May 2009 |accessdate=12 September 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140403102304/http://www.monstersandcritics.com/people/news/article_1474460.php/Karl_Lagerfeld_selects_Lily_Allen_for_Chanel_handbag_layout |archivedate=3 April 2014}}</ref>

2009年9月，莉莉称其正在考虑开启演艺职涯，而不再为其唱片合同续约，并称“尚无计划”制作新专辑。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nme.com/news/lily-allen/47490|title=Lily Allen: 'I won't release another album'|date=24 September 2009|work=NME|accessdate=22 September 2014|archive-date=2016-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160409120837/http://www.nme.com/news/lily-allen/47490|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2010年9月，她进行了两年半来的最后一场表演，在英国[[伦敦|伦敦]]的[[温布利球场|温布利球场]]助阵[[缪斯乐队|缪斯乐队]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gigwise.com/news/58350/muse-play-spectacular-opening-gig-at-wembley-stadium |title=Muse Play Spectacular Opening Gig at Wembley Stadium |publisher=Gigwise |date=10 September 2010 |accessdate=7 May 2014 |archive-date=2019-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129235654/https://www.gigwise.com/news/58350/muse-play-spectacular-opening-gig-at-wembley-stadium |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2010年6月，她参与了[[史提芬·保罗·曼德尔森|格林教授]]的英国前五单曲《{{tsl|en|Just Be Good to Green||Just Be Good to Green}}》的合唱。2010年9月15日，莉莉·艾伦与其姐妹开张了她们自己的服装店，名为“Lucy in Disguise”。同年11月，在《[[每日郵報|每日邮报]]》刊登她的住宅照片后，她以侵犯[[隐私权|隐私权]]和[[侵犯版權|侵犯版权]]为由起诉了《每日邮报》的母公司{{tsl|en|Associated Newspapers||Associated Newspapers}}。<ref>{{cite news |author=Mark Sweney |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2010/nov/29/lily-allen-mail-legal-action |title=Lily Allen takes legal action over Mail Online article |work=The Guardian |location=London |date=29 November 2010 |accessdate=24 July 2011 |archive-date=2018-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180921074527/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2010/nov/29/lily-allen-mail-legal-action |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在此期间，莉莉专注于成家，但并为完全舍弃音乐事业。2011年1月，她在[[索尼音樂娛樂|索尼音乐]]的财政支持下创立了自己的唱片公司{{tsl|en|In the Name Of (record label)||In the Name Of}}。该公司与纽约{{tsl|en|noise pop||noise pop}}二人组合{{tsl|en|Cults (band)||Cults}}签下了第一笔合约。<ref>{{cite news |author=Michaels, Sean |url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2011/jan/21/lily-allen-launches-record-label |title=Lily Allen launches own record label |work=The Guardian |date=21 January 2011 |accessdate=24 July 2011 |location=London |archive-date=2020-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803073428/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2011/jan/21/lily-allen-launches-record-label |dead-url=no }}</ref> 接下来的一个月，她开始为将在2012年与于伦敦[[西区剧院|西区剧院]]上演的音乐剧版《{{tsl|en|Bridget Jones' Diary (musical)||Bridget Jones's Diary}}》写歌。<ref name="BridgetJones">{{cite news |last=Perricone |first=Kathleen |url=http://articles.nydailynews.com/2011-07-05/entertainment/29759461_1_lily-allen-ups-and-downs-songs |title=Lily Allen 'nearly finished' writing songs for 'Bridget Jones's Diary' stage musical, to debut 2012 |work=Daily News |location=New York |date=5 July 2011 |accessdate=24 July 2011 |archive-date=2012-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120603140158/http://articles.nydailynews.com/2011-07-05/entertainment/29759461_1_lily-allen-ups-and-downs-songs |dead-url=no }}</ref> 同年，[[提潘|T-Pain]]使用了莉莉歌曲《{{tsl|en|Who'd Have Known||Who'd Have Known}}》中的主歌部分作为前者专辑《Revolver》第二首单曲《5 O'Clock》的副歌。《Who'd Have Known》由[[维兹·卡利法|维兹·卡利法]]参与合唱，发行于2011年9月并在[[告示牌百强单曲榜|Billboard百强单曲榜]]中名列第十；这是莉莉在美国的第一首前十歌曲。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/1155844/rihannas-we-found-love-is-2011s-singers-longest-chart-topping-hot-100-song|title=Rihanna's 'We Found Love ' Is 2011's, Singer's Longest Chart-Topping Hot 100 Song|work=Billboard|accessdate=14 September 2017|archive-date=2018-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180921114943/https://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/1155844/rihannas-we-found-love-is-2011s-singers-longest-chart-topping-hot-100-song|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===2012年至今 ：第三张录音室专辑===
2012年6月20日，艾伦说她在工作室与制作人Greg Kurstin制作新的音乐。<ref>{{cite web|title=Lily Allen back in the studio with Greg Kurstin|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a388583/lily-allen-back-in-the-studio-with-greg-kurstin.html|accessdate=19 June 2012|archive-date=2013-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131113231947/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a388583/lily-allen-back-in-the-studio-with-greg-kurstin.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Lily Allen back in the studio with Greg Kurstin|url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/lily-allen/357621-lily-allen-twitter-popjustice-studio-greg-kurstin-pro-green|accessdate=19 June 2012|archive-date=2013-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131118094403/http://www.mtv.co.uk/news/lily-allen/357621-lily-allen-twitter-popjustice-studio-greg-kurstin-pro-green|dead-url=no}}</ref> 她将艺名从“莉莉·艾伦”（Lily Allen）改为“莉莉·罗斯·库珀”（Lily Rose Cooper）。<ref>{{cite web|title=Lily Allen Changes Professional Name To Lily Rose Cooper|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/lily-allen-changes-professional-name-to-lily-rose-cooper-20120802|publisher=Rolling Stone|accessdate=2 August 2012|archive-date=2014-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106214310/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/lily-allen-changes-professional-name-to-lily-rose-cooper-20120802|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在2012年9月发行的[[粉红佳人|粉红佳人]]专辑《[[有愛有真相|The Truth About Love]]（有爱有真相）》中，艾伦与其合唱了单曲《True Love》。
2012年10月，艾伦称她在工作室“往墙上面扔东西，看看有没有什么会粘在上面……（注：指她正在毫无顾忌地做各种音乐的尝试）能够这样心无旁骛地工作真是不错。”<ref name="q_dec_2012">Q magazine. October 2012. Coming Up / Also Tweaking. P. 23</ref> 在2013年2月，她在一场巴黎时装表演（由马克·罗森制作），并且透露称新专辑在2013年底发行，专辑以“她身为母亲的经历”为灵感。<ref>[http://www.independent.ie/entertainment/music/allen-proud-of-stage-mumback-29101362.html "Allen proud of stage 'mumback'"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.independent.ie/entertainment/music/allen-proud-of-stage-mumback-29101362.html |date=20131203041935 }}, The ''Irish Independent'', 28 February 2013. Retrieved 16 June 2013.</ref>2013年8月，她将其艺名改回到“莉莉·艾伦”，发推说新音乐将会“很快”来临。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/music/news/lily-allen-new-music-coming-soon-29536988.html |title=Lily Allen: new music coming soon? Belfast Telegraph 29 August 2013 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archive-date=2013-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131113232208/http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/music/news/lily-allen-new-music-coming-soon-29536988.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
2013年11月，艾伦录制了[[Keane|Keane（基音乐队）]]歌曲《Somewhere Only We Know》的翻唱版本作为[[:en:John_Lewis_(department_store)|约翰·刘易斯百货商场]]圣诞广告的背景乐。这支单曲在iTunes上以数位下载形式发行，并迅速登上英国iTunes下载榜第一名。2013年11月12日，新单曲《[[Hard_Out_Here|Hard Out Here]]》的MV在艾伦的官方YouTube账号上发行。並在同月18日於iTunes上公開發售。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nme.com/news/lily-allen/73786 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |archive-date=2013-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131115023521/http://www.nme.com/news/lily-allen/73786 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

